## Delegation Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define the task and its scope, deadlines, and success criteria
- [ ] 2. Assess who is best suited: skills, capacity, and development goals
- [ ] 3. Communicate the task with context and expectations
- [ ] 4. Agree on checkpoints and review milestones
- [ ] 5. Provide support without taking back the work
- [ ] 6. Review outcomes and provide feedback

## Key Inputs
- Task: {{task}}
- Team Members: {{team_members}} (skills, capacity, development areas)
- Deadline: {{deadline}}
- Success Criteria: {{success_criteria}}
- Context: {{context}}
